          .row.row-controls
            .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
              form
                .checkbox
                  label
                    input(type='checkbox')
                    | I agree and accept these terms and conditions
          .row.row-controls
            .col-md-2.col-md-offset-2
              a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-block(href='#' role='button').text-uppercase Back
            .col-md-6
              a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.btn-block(href='#' role='button').text-uppercase Accept and continue

        .tab-pane#tab3
          .row
            .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
              h2.text-uppercase Ethereum wallet
              hr
              form
                .form-group
                  label(for='wallet') What Ethereum wallet you are using?
                  select.form-control#wallet(aria-describedby='wallet-help')
                    option(value='coinbase') Coinbase
                    option(value='my-ether-wallet') MyEtherWallet
                    option(value='other') Other wallets
                  span.help-block#wallet-help Tokens are compatible with some Ethereum wallets only. You cannot use an address from a cryptocurrency exchange.
                  .alert.alert-info(role='alert')
                    p #[span.glyphicon.glyphicon-question-sign(aria-hidden='true')] 
                      a(href='#') For the instructions and compatible wallets see this page
          .row.row-controls
            .col-md-2.col-md-offset-2
              a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-block(href='#' role='button').text-uppercase Back
            .col-md-6
              a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.btn-block(href='#' role='button').text-uppercase Submit and continue

        .tab-pane#tab4
          .row
            .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
              h2.text-uppercase Notification email
              hr
              form
                .form-group
                  label(for='email') Your email address
                  input.form-control#email(type='email' placeholder='example@example.org' aria-describedby='email-help')
                  span.help-block#email-help You will be notified when your tokens are available. We won't disclose your email to third parties.
          .row.row-controls
            .col-md-2.col-md-offset-2
              a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-block(href='#' role='button').text-uppercase Back
            .col-md-6
              a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.btn-block(href='#' role='button').text-uppercase Submit and continue

        .tab-pane#tab5
          .row
            .col-md-8.col-md-offset-2
              h2.text-uppercase Buyer information
              hr
              form
                .form-group
                  label(for='name') Your full name
                  input.form-control#name(type='text')
                .form-group
                  label(for='company-name') Company name
                  input.form-control#company-name(type='text' aria-describedby='company-name-help')
                  span.help-block#company-name-help For incorporated buyers only, otherwise leave empty
                .form-group
                  label(for='phone') Phone number
                  input.form-control#phone(type='tel')
                .form-group
                  label(for='address') Address
                  input.form-control#address(type='text' aria-describedby='address-help')
                  span.help-block#address-help Street address, postal code, city
                .form-group
                  label(for='country') Country
                  select.form-control#country(aria-describedby='country-help')
                    option(value='dominican-republic') Dominican Republic
                    option(value='other') Other countries
                  span.help-block#country-help This information is collected for contractual purposes only
          .row.row-controls
            .col-md-2.col-md-offset-2
              a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-block(href='#' role='button').text-uppercase Back
            .col-md-6
              a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.btn-block(href='#' role='button').text-uppercase Submit and continue

        .tab-pane#tab6
          .row
            .col-md-12
              h2.text-uppercase Deposit
              hr
          .row
            .col-md-6
              form
                .form-group
                  label(for='deposit-address').text-uppercase Address:
                  span.input-group
                    a.input-group-addon.btn.btn-default(href='#' role='button') Copy
                    textarea.form-control.no-resize#deposit-address(readonly) 0x123f681646d4a755815f9cb19e1acc8565a0c2ac
                .form-group
                  label(for='deposit-data').text-uppercase Data: #[span.label.label-warning Required]
                  .input-group
                    a.input-group-addon.btn.btn-default(href='#' role='button') Copy
                    textarea.form-control.no-resize#deposit-data(required readonly) 0x99e9376c000000000000000000000c8328e07d1644c83818838579c590cb5
                .form-group
                  // There is weird spacing between T and semicolon, looking like no spacing at all.
                  // Trying to fix that with span.spaced
                  label(for='deposit-gas-limit').text-uppercase Gas limi#[span.spaced t:] #[span.label.label-warning Required]
                  .input-group
                    a.input-group-addon.btn.btn-default(href='#' role='button') Copy
                    input.form-control#deposit-gas-limit(type='text' required readonly value='260300')
                .form-group
                  label(for='deposit-gas-price').text-uppercase Gas price (GWEI):
                  .input-group
                    a.input-group-addon.btn.btn-default(href='#' role='button') Copy
                    input.form-control#deposit-gas-price(type='text' readonly value='30')
            .col-md-6#deposit-help
              label(for='deposit-help').text-uppercase Instructions:
              p Minimum payment: 20 ETH.
              p You'll receive 20% discount.
              p Make Ethereum transaction using given personal payment details and your whitelisted Ethereum address. You need to fill in ALL payment details in your wallet:
                ul
                  li Amount ETH (more than minimum)
                  li Address
                  li Gas limit
                  li Data
              .alert.alert-info(role='alert')
                p #[span.glyphicon.glyphicon-question-sign(aria-hidden='true')] 
                  strong.text-uppercase Need help?
                  p
                    a(href='#') See how to make a transaction to an Ethereum token presale          
          .row.row-controls
            .col-md-2.col-md-offset-2
              a.btn.btn-default.btn-lg.btn-block(href='#' role='button').text-uppercase Back
            .col-md-6
              a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg.btn-block(href='#' role='button').text-uppercase Go to the Dashboard